\id HEB - Sembeleke SAMBERIGI PNG HEBREWS 01 22/3/91 Macnaughtan 
\h HIBULU 
\toc1 Hibulu Ketiso tapake paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee 
\toc2 Hibulu 
\toc3 Hibulu 
\mt1 Hibulu Ketiso tapake paęž‰taęž‰ tapaeyeke wapee  
\c 1  
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ la kaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande ambi sanake sanake aneketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hoto eleke elekemaęž‰ make mandane hau manumaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo potopede haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ atekenaęž‰ ateketonu paęž‰taęž‰ la halaęž‰tiki pu hayekeme.  
\v 2 Kutu pieke patetaęž‰ pa ame do wetepe nanetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto Eiyekenaęž‰ kikimaęž‰taęž‰ do kenke ya yaaponaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyao wepia winaęž‰ laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo paelo paęž‰laęž‰ nanetaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao kilu tombuao haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki mea hayekeme.  
\v 3 Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke nikinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰ hali hataęž‰ make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handeke kone make hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wele wotu piki pimaęž‰ do kenke ya paeyao miniliao halaęž‰me.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰ hau tieke  
\p
\v 4 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ mo enisolo tonunaęž‰ biki lombei piki biki mieke tupaęž‰ ipiki make mo enisolo tonu lombei pao hayekeme.  
\v 5 Ambaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰ dupae  
\q1 Neketaęž‰ ya wekie. IĚ± ametaęž‰ nakaęž‰ Apaęž‰ halome leekeme.  
\p Kutupa pa yaapo pao pimaęž‰ make alotaęž‰  
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ hano ipikitaęž‰ ya weki halieke  
\m leeke pitaęž‰ mo enisolomanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ leeke yeke yekea. Diaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kotoeki na piekepate ipikaęž‰ mupeke weki do kenkenaęž‰ tapaalo pieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ pi dupa leekeme.  
\q1 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ enisolo tonu paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ mo Weki paęž‰taęž‰ pandaęž‰ puniaaso ipikaęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ lalimikie  
\m leeke patetaęž‰  
\v 7 mo enisolo tapake ikinaęž‰taęž‰ pi dupa leekeme.  
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enisolo tonutaęž‰ mo po tupaęž‰ wepiaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ tapake tonu ti uleke tupaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyekenaęž‰taęž‰ dupa leekeme.  
\q1 O Kodaęž‰ nakaęž‰ kilu tombuao halo pele ekitaęž‰ na paeke pa u halieke.  
\q1 Nakaęž‰ tikitiki piki haumaęž‰taęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke hao haleme.   
\q1
\v 9 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ epeke hau paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ puki wopu pelepate hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ honditi wopu peleme.  
\q1 Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ nakaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ hataęž‰ neke mea mo nakaęž‰ yankeke tonu lombei piki some halenaęž‰ tombo kitolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ peaasaęž‰ honku nakaęž‰ kitawayaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 10 Kutaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make alotaęž‰  
\q1 Tekehalio. Mo hande panake kini pu miki ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande yu paeyao wepitolo hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ mo ya nane ulaęž‰ alemanu paeyao make wepeme.   
\q1
\v 11 Koto alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ pa alu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate neketaęž‰ pa hao halipikie.  
\q1 Kutu pulu pelepate mo ale manutaęž‰ dau sinkipaęž‰ pa pa pu pulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ sinkipaęž‰ pa pa pu pelieke.   
\q1
\v 12 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ mo hande daumanu pankaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ pankaęž‰ pilipikie.  
\q1 Kutupa nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ale manutaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ dau topo piteleme tupaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ topo pilipikie.  
\q1 Koto ale manutaęž‰ kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate neketaęž‰ topu maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pu make nakaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki na paeyo piki pa hao halipikie leekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ leeke pi maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ dupa  
\q1 Nakaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki tapaketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ anke oto paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ laano neketaęž‰ ya popeke kiki nanemaęž‰ hando pitie leekeme.  
\m Koto pitaęž‰ mo hande enisolomanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ leeke yeke yekea. Diaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 14 Mo enisolo paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki mulu peleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ temokomanu na halemeke yekea.   
\c 2  
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea deto halaęž‰eki kaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau tieke  
\p
\v 1 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ niki ipilipa lopa mo opumaęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao puaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ koto pitaęž‰ hone otaęž‰ wopu wia miniki hamanaęž‰ peaęž‰peke alee.  
\v 2 Mo enisolo haliwekimaęž‰ nikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ atekenaęž‰ ateketonu paęž‰taęž‰ la halemeke pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi yeekeme. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ koto pi opua na hao o homu pea na hao pieke some hayeke handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mieke yenkitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pu hayeke hau anaęž‰ piki yenki meaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 3 Kutu pimiki ekinaęž‰taęž‰ pa niki make mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ lolo kaęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki tiekenaęž‰ hone wopu na umaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ekipa mo niki paęž‰taęž‰ kulu paęž‰laęž‰ hoke yenki wendulumaęž‰pe. Tekehalimaęž‰ kone do kaęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki peneme yaeyekeme. Koto ekitaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leeke pi opimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ do pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pie laa niki paęž‰taęž‰ wopu la kimime.  
\v 4 Kutaa make koto ikanaęž‰maęž‰ la kimi pi manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ pie hone wiomono yeketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ na handeke haumanu make taęž‰taęž‰ piki haumanu make piekeme. Kutupa make ipikaęž‰ hone pieke ekinaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ haumanu pa hameke hakaęž‰taęž‰pao telipatiki pu hayekeme.   
\s1 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miomono yeke nikaęž‰ you halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ halaęž‰me  
\p
\v 5 Do ipilieke lo halomaęž‰ kenke panakeeki handeteke haenaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ enisolomanu na mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 6 Koto hau na piekepatetaęž‰ mo hande Baibolo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ wape maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ dupae  
\q1 Kodaęž‰o. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ halitaęž‰ aleke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe.  
\q1 Ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa handeteke halenaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ eki paęž‰laęž‰pe.   
\q1
\v 7 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hali wepitolo hataęž‰ mo hande enisolo oto paęž‰taęž‰ hosiki haenaęž‰ wepia haenaęž‰ leke yekepate  
\q1 paa wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki tieke pitaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki tieke yaapo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dopuaeyekeme.   
\q1
\v 8 Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handeteke haenaęž‰ leme laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\m Kodaęž‰maęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handeteke haenaęž‰ wepiekeme mo Baibolomaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao tapao paęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰me. Koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto alaęž‰pate pa ametaęž‰ halimaęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao handeteke halaęž‰me ekitaęž‰ na handolomaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Pate pa Yesu handolomaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ anketeke mea homaenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki enisolo manunaęž‰ oto nane hosiki haenaęž‰ leekeme. Pate ametaęž‰ nikaęž‰naęž‰ tanda tieke mea homeeke yekemaęž‰ koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki tieke pitaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaasaęž‰eki tieke yaapo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ dopuaeyeke ekitaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao wepia winaęž‰ laa epeke handeteke halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wekiwandiki eleke eleke ipikaęž‰ hepeni kenke seliapo nane haenaęž‰ yeke ikaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki meĚ±aĚ±yaęž‰ hali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ tanda tieke haleeke ekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ikaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hali haenaęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hau epeke piekeme.  
\v 11 Mo wandaęž‰hali yako pea haenaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ hali make mo epeaaleke yako pea haleme wandaęž‰hali iki paeyaonaęž‰ Apaęž‰taęž‰ homeke homeke halaęž‰me. Yesumaęž‰ koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ koto wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ kame tonue loluekemaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ na homeke lo halaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alo alotaęž‰  
\q1 Mo nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pieki paeyaotaęž‰ ya kame tonu paęž‰taęž‰ la halueke.  
\q1 Nakaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mombilimi alenaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lawaalueke leekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Paa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ make alotaęž‰  
\q1 IĚ±taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ti lao halueke laa  
\m paa make alotaęž‰  
\q1 IĚ±taęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kiaęž‰ weki wandiki tonu ameĚ±leĚ± do aęž‰pa halo handaęž‰e leekeme.   
\s1 Yesu otaęž‰ hali hayekeeki  
\p
\v 14 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Mo wekiwandikie leaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kenke loke hake wandaęž‰hali haemeke yeke handaataęž‰ ipiki make ikaęž‰ loke mea kenke hali leke hayekeme. Koto loke mea ipikaęž‰ homeeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wele handeteke halaęž‰ hali Sadani bepolaluekemaęž‰ yeke piekeme.  
\v 15 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo homaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ nate paeyao niki tonkao halaęž‰ hautaęž‰ Yesu ipikaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaalaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ enisolo tonu tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yeke na piekepate mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tapake wekiwandiki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ piekeme laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\m
\v 17 Koto hau puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ hau paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hameke tonu leke hayekeme. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ peaęž‰peke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lake Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni peao halaęž‰ hali haluekemaęž‰ kutu piekeme. Wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyawaenaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ hambaasotaęž‰ kutu piekeme.  
\v 18 Koto ekinaęž‰ ipiki make mo la handaęž‰laęž‰eki manunaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu mu hayeke handaataęž‰ ame make mo la handaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki aĚ±iĚ± tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 3  
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ Mosesi lombei piki hali halaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi laęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ ya Ketiso kame tonuo nikaęž‰ hone tu lao halomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ yeni peao halaęž‰ You hali pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ tapaeyeke hali Yesu peneme yaaso hataęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu u hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 2 Hande Mosesimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ e paeyao maęž‰ndaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lake hataęž‰ pa otaęž‰ epeke e pokaeyeke tupaęž‰ Yesu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaaluekemaęž‰ peaęž‰peke yeke ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lake paeyao otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ kone pokaeyekeme.  
\v 3 Da seliapo homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰eliaęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ da seliapoe laa hotu halo pelemepate pa mo da aęž‰eliaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki homeke epeke da aęž‰elaęž‰ halie laa ipikaęž‰ biki homeke kende wilieke. Mo da aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki kende wilie tupaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ bikimaęž‰ Mosesinaęž‰ biki otaęž‰ lombei piki biki tieke winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 4 Da paeyaotaęž‰ halimaęž‰ kone aęž‰etaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeya tapaonaęž‰ wepia winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ sometaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ homeke halaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mosesimaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ e epeke tupaęž‰ pokaeyekeme. Kutu pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wetepe lapeke yeke pi manutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ la haleekeme.  
\v 6 Mosesitaęž‰ pa e pokaasaęž‰ hali homeke hayekepate Ketisotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke yaalo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali otaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰me. Koto handeteke halaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ nikie. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ otaęž‰ pealieke hone witaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ aelaęž‰ baasaęž‰ hau yaapo aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu miniki haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ alome.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoto pitulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 7 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ kinki pitolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Ame do natenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰   
\q1
\v 8 kotaęž‰ mo hande ikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ atekenaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ puki takaęž‰laaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi na opiki nono pimiki tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make pi na opiki nono na peaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\q1 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hande hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ haemeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ koto alo hau manumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ piliaęž‰ hau handuluekemaęž‰ makea handemekeme.   
\q1
\v 9 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ bapi paeyao hali tieke yaaponaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ puaęž‰ hau tieke tieketaęž‰ pa mo handolo hataęž‰ kone ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paa makea handemekeme leekeme.   
\q1
\v 10 Kutu pimi ekinaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Do wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hoto paeyao IĚ± kiaaso ya pi ulu ekimanu kiao na opu halememe.  
\v 11 Koto pimi ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mineke tieke pankolo otaęž‰ topo piaęž‰peke na yeke pi tieke laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰  
\q1 Koto wandaęž‰hali hoto pitinaęž‰ halueke laa pi laęž‰ ulu kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na pelimikie laa pi laęž‰ ulumaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 12 Aiyo. Kame tonuo. Iki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰laluekemaęž‰ hoke hone na tulaasaęž‰ hoke hone wiaamaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 13 Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ mo hoke haumaęž‰ iki makeao haamaęž‰naęž‰ laa ikaęž‰ puki takaęž‰lawaamaęž‰naęž‰ nate paeyao ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone epeke pi manumaęž‰ tikitiki ya alualu pu hapaęž‰peke. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ Ame do natee laęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ waleke kitolo aleketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto alaęž‰ hau pu hamanaęž‰e.  
\v 14 Mo hande nikaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hone ti laomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lake homolo kiaęž‰naluekemaęž‰ honkopu hao hataęž‰ miniki hao hamanaęž‰e. Koto hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketiso ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao tunaa halomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 15 Hande kinki pitolo alaęž‰ pitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ ipulu ipulu hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ dupae  
\q1 Ame Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hande ikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ atekenaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ puki takaęž‰laaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi na opiki nono pimiki tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make pi na opiki nono na peaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 16 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opitolo hataęž‰ kone kiaemeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ epi ameda yekea. Ikitaęž‰ mo hande Mosesimaęž‰ Idiepi kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao hatuku peeke wandaęž‰hali paeyao diaęž‰yeke yekea.  
\v 17 Bapi hali tieke yaapo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ epi ameda paęž‰taęž‰ mineke pankaęž‰tiki pu hayekea. Mo hande hapu hayeke alenaęž‰ hoke hau pea homo tandepemeke wandaęž‰hali diaęž‰yeke yekea.  
\v 18 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi tieke laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Koto wandaęž‰hali hoto pitinaęž‰ halueke laa pi laęž‰ ulu kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na pelimikie laa pi laęž‰ ulume leeke ekitaęž‰ epinaęž‰ leeke yekea. Mo hande ipikaęž‰ pi kiaemeke wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 19 Ikaęž‰ hone na tulaemekeme. Ikaęž‰ kutu pimiki ekimaęž‰ kone mo hande hoto pitinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ halueke laa pi laęž‰ wieke kenke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ puaęž‰peke na yekeme. Koto ekitaęž‰ do la kitaęž‰leke opitolomaęž‰me.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kulueke laa pi laęž‰ wieke hoto pitaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ ame make nikinaęž‰ pa u pelia halaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ iki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ koto pi laęž‰ wiekeeki wendiaamaęž‰naęž‰ kimelemaęž‰ hao hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 2 Mo Pi Seliapotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opimiki tupaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make opu haomaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke opimikipate kone hone tulao na miniki haemeke ekimaęž‰ mo pimaęž‰taęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke na yekeme.   
\p
\v 3 Kutu piekepate ame nikitaęž‰ hone tulao halomaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki talo hataęž‰ hoto pitaęž‰peke laa leeke ekinaęž‰ mu halomaęž‰me. Ambaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pimaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ kone alotaęž‰  
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mineke tieke pankolo otaęž‰ topo piaęž‰peke na yeke pi tieke laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰  
\q1 Koto wandaęž‰hali hoto pitinaęž‰ halueke laa pi laęž‰ ulu kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na pelimikie laa pi laęž‰ ulumaęž‰ loaęž‰me leekeme.  
\m Koto leekepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenke wepia paeyao paeyeke hoki nanetaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e otaęž‰ paeyekeme.  
\v 4 Mo Baibolo tukiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo watake hataęž‰ natenaęž‰ pitaęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Mo watake hataęž‰ natetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e poko tunkula hoto pitiekeme laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\m
\v 5 Do hande hoto pitinaęž‰e laa wapenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ pi kone paa yaapo peao dupa laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Koto wandaęž‰hali hoto pitinaęž‰ halueke laa pi laęž‰ ulu kenke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ na pelimikie laa pi laęž‰ ulumaęž‰ loaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 6 Mo Pi Seliapo titinaęž‰ opimiki wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone na tulaemeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hoto pitaęž‰pekeeki na mimikime. Kutu pimikitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ pa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo koto hoto pilaęž‰eki miaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 7 Koto miaęž‰pekeeki otaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Ame koto natee leekeme. Do wapenaęž‰ ambaęž‰ loaęž‰ Baibolo pitaęž‰ bapi wopu paeyeke hoki nane Deipidimaęž‰ laęž‰naęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ dupae  
\q1 Ame do natenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make opimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ puki takaęž‰laaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi na opiki nono na peaęž‰peke leekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Diosuamaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke hoto pilaęž‰ nate haleaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ulumee pi na lolo piaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ watake hataęž‰ natenaęž‰ hoto pilieke tupaęž‰ pa niki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoto pitaęž‰peke natetaęž‰ pa wiaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone witolomaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Epi amedamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ halueke laa laęž‰ wieke hoto pitaęž‰pekeeki aęž‰ndaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e poko tunkula hoto pitieke tupaęž‰ koto halimaęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ e poko tunkula hoto pitilieke.  
\v 11 Mo hande ambaęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hone wopu na tulaemeke ekimaęž‰ pu hoeyaemeke tupaęž‰ niki make kutu paamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ mo hoto pitaęž‰peke nate muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu wia pumanaęž‰e.   
\p
\v 12 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ daęž‰taa hataęž‰ e wopu poko halaęž‰me. Mo pimaęž‰taęž‰ hande kake yaapo hake bainasi kone lombei pea ne ne wopu halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo pimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali pondaęž‰paęž‰ awa ikaęž‰ temoko pitaęž‰ hone teke yaapo tukikinaęž‰ opolo pua tekili peao make ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ holiki kilikalu yaapo paęž‰nkaęž‰paęž‰ lia tekili pea alu make peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ honenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu tikitiki yawao halaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ na handenaęž‰ yeke alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰mbao pankaęž‰ wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Diaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰leketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰taęž‰ mo wepia ulaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao otaęž‰ peneme yao lumbupa ulaęž‰me. Kutupa niki paeyaomaęž‰ nikaęž‰ pumaęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yaalumeke.   
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ nikaęž‰ yeni peao halaęž‰ you hali tieke  
\p
\v 14 Koto paęž‰leke handaataęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Yeni peao halaęž‰ You hali tieketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke Yesutaęž‰ mo hepeni da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambeeke yeke handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo nikaęž‰ hone tulaalomaęž‰eki wopu handeteke hao hamanaęž‰e.  
\v 15 Nikaęž‰ Yeni peao halaęž‰ You halimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ honkopu na hake dete piki haumanu handaa aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ na homolo paęž‰laęž‰ hali diaęž‰me. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Yeni peao halaęž‰ You halitaęž‰ mo niki la handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paeyaomaęž‰ ipiki make la handetiki piekepate hoke hau homeke siki maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na piekeme.  
\v 16 Nikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ natemanu epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ aelaęž‰ bao hataęž‰ mo pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homo halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ pomanaęž‰e.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Hali homeke mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ you hali haenaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali hao pinaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondo maĚ±leke lu miaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me. Mo yeni peaasaęž‰ you halimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau aęž‰mbawaluekemaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lia halaęž‰laęž‰eki make totopo yolepiki ale halaęž‰laęž‰eki make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Mo sometaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hau manumaęž‰ make detepiki hali hataęž‰ kone mo pi ulaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu mataalo hataęž‰ pu hoeyao haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ yopu kimelemaęž‰ tambaęž‰ mu hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 3 Ipiki make detepiki hali hataęž‰ kone mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke haumaęž‰ homeke diaęž‰ yekepate ipikaęž‰ hoke hau make aęž‰mbawaenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lia halaęž‰tiki piaęž‰peke yekeme.   
\p
\v 4 Mo yeni peaasaęž‰ hali hasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ biki tieke minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone ipiki maĚ±leke lia hapeke na yeliepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi lelie ekinaęž‰ homeke ipikaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ hali hapeke yelieke. Pa mo hande Etoni wi leeke tupaęž‰ kone wi lelieke.   
\p
\v 5 Mandake tupaęž‰ Yesumaęž‰ mo yeni peao halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki tieketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone na miekepate pa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Neketaęž‰ ya wekie. Ametaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ nakaęž‰ Apaęž‰ halome leekeme.   
\p
\v 6 Kutupa make Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Baibolo maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Neketaęž‰ mo hande Melekisedeke hataęž‰ pieke tupaęž‰ bapi paeyaonaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ hali hao halipikie leekeme.   
\p
\v 7 Yesumaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ipiki meaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰peke yeke Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yeni pieke ekimaęž‰ make honke leeke ekimaęž‰ make eĚ± wi tieke laa eĚ± pankeke lopolo haenaęž‰ yeni piekeme. Koto yenitaęž‰ homu pikimaęž‰ pieke handaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ opiekeme.  
\v 8 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke hayekepate ipikaęž‰ homu pieke ekitaęž‰ mo hande tandamaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki mieke yeke ekimaęž‰ hone wiekeme.  
\v 9 Ipikitaęž‰ koto hau paeyaonaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰ pieketaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homaa pi opu haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tekehali hayekeme.  
\v 10 Kutu pieke handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Neketaęž‰ mo hande Melekisedeke hataęž‰ pieke tupaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ you hali hao halipikie laa peneme yao leekeme.   
\s1 Andu nalaęž‰ wekiwandiki tupaęž‰ na hao hamanaęž‰ leekeeki  
\p
\v 11  Do haunaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi eleke eleke otaęž‰ wopu lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pate ikitaęž‰ hone aĚ±iĚ± na miaęž‰peke yaęž‰leke handaa mo pimanu walaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰leke paasomaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hamenaęž‰ yeke nate tieke anaęž‰naęž‰ wiaęž‰pate kone pa mo hande wekiwandiki sunu paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hosiki pi sunu maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ paa walenaęž‰ lapeke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me. Epeke takaęž‰lake nemanu no hapaęž‰peke yolo paęž‰laęž‰pate pa andu homeke no halememe.  
\v 13 Wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ andu homeke napeke yaęž‰laęž‰ some hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo sometaęž‰ mo hande hoke hau epeke hau yaapo telipea haluekemaęž‰ hone na wiki pa pu haleme wekiwandiki leke halememe.  
\v 14 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate mo hoke hau pitaęž‰ epeke hau yaapo talo talo pea epeke tupaęž‰ telipea haleme keileke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo epeke takaęž‰lake ne tupaęž‰ no halimikie.   
\c 6  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande titi panake paęž‰taęž‰ opumaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pi manunaęž‰ homeke na ambula u hake pa winaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi mandane ekimanu make handaęž‰tia pomanaęž‰e. Da aęž‰eyomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ oni hande ambaęž‰ nokopomaęž‰ da kaęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pa yoka nokaęž‰paęž‰tiki nokaęž‰paęž‰tiki peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ kone nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ titinaęž‰ pimanu make mo teke na wiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu minaęž‰paęž‰lao hone laęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pimanu make  
\v 2 bapitaisi pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau manunaęž‰ pi walaęž‰laęž‰eki make younaęž‰ kiki wia yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu make homa paa tiaasaęž‰ hau make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi yokaalu pea mo honiki na paeke homo halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ tapaalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu make koto ambaęž‰ hande titinaęž‰ walomaęž‰ pimanu na ambula u hake  
\v 3 pa mandane ekimanu make handaęž‰tia pomanaęž‰e. Kutu piomono Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ waleke kiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ putia polumeke.   
\p
\v 4 Mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki minaęž‰paęž‰laemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ pa ekipa ikaęž‰ puki laęž‰kaęž‰la hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ tulaenaęž‰ handaęž‰ mea epomanaęž‰pe. Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ haemeke handa make mo hepeni nanemaęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ hau ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ pea handemeke handa make mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ telipea yekeeki make mimiki handaataęž‰  
\v 5 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi mea pea handa epekeeki yeke handaataęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me hone make wimiki handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wetepe epolo paęž‰laęž‰ natenaęž‰ wele tiekenaęž‰ wele wataa handemeke handaataęž‰  
\v 6 kotaęž‰ koto hau paeyao pea hoki nanetaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki minaęž‰paęž‰lao lopeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki paa laęž‰kaęž‰la aęž‰pa hone tulaenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ paa hatuku aęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Diaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ koto peleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ mo aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ ipiki paa liki nono pitelememe.   
\p
\v 7 Kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ lako nalo hataęž‰ mo e handeteke halaęž‰ halinaęž‰ ne anekemaęž‰ opaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kenketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ kenkee.  
\v 8 Pate mo kaĚ±ęž‰laĚ±ęž‰taęž‰ o hoke ambu homeke opaęž‰laęž‰ kenketaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoeyaalo paęž‰laęž‰eki make teke paęž‰taęž‰ ulume. Koto hoke ambu opitaęž‰laęž‰ kenketaęž‰ timaęž‰ yankilieke.   
\p
\v 9 Nikaęž‰ puki piki yankeke titio. Iki paęž‰taęž‰ dupiki pi tieke alomaęž‰pate pa mo daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mea aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu pu haleme ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto piteme wandaęž‰hali iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na witolomaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Kodaęž‰taęž‰ homeke paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone ulaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ epeke e pokaęž‰lemekeeki make ikaęž‰ Ketiso kame tonu tambaęž‰ mimieki make ame do pa tambaęž‰ mu haleme ekimaęž‰ make koto hau paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki peneme yaasaęž‰me. Koto piteme ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ pinaęž‰e hone wilimieki iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pinaęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homeke honkopu hao hataęž‰ mo hande epeke haumanu pa peaęž‰tiki pu hamenaęž‰ niki hone wopu paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 12 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰ homeleme wandaęž‰hali hamenaęž‰ niki hone na paęž‰laęž‰me. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ mo hande mandane wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hone tulaemeke haumaęž‰ make ikaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ yu wia haemeke haumaęž‰ make koto hau yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekimanu mu haemekeme. Koto wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰ muemenaęž‰ hone witolomaęž‰me.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ yaalo pieke pi laęž‰ wiekeeki  
\p
\v 13 Mo hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke dinaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ manda halaęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ diaęž‰ yeke handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki kone laa otaęž‰ pi alo loaęž‰me laa pi laęž‰ wiekeme.  
\v 14 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke epeaotaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hoki nane halo peleme tapaketaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu haenaęž‰ lolueke pitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ otaęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ witolome leekeme.  
\v 15 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi laęž‰ wieke ale muluekemaęž‰ yu wia hayeke handaataęž‰ koto pi laęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ miekeme.   
\p
\v 16 Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ pi loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo paeyaonaęž‰ bikimanu tombuao otaęž‰ manda halaęž‰ biki ulaęž‰ halinaęž‰ biki laa laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pi leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pimaęž‰taęž‰ mo pi yokaęž‰ alualu piki pi aleme ekimanu pa tunkulalieke.  
\v 17 Kodaęž‰ make mo hande pi laęž‰ wiekeeki mulu peleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puluekee laa laęž‰ wiekeeki otaęž‰ topo na peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hali keke witaęž‰laęž‰ pimaęž‰ apaęž‰tao laęž‰ wiekeme.  
\v 18 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ koto topo peaęž‰peke na yo yayapiki pi na lo peaęž‰peke yekeeki yaapo winaęž‰ leekeme. Ipikaęž‰ oto nane tinki pa halomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali nikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone ti lalomaęž‰eki otaęž‰ miniki hamono yeke do koto pi yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ puki tieke wopu mea tialaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Do hone ti lalomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ temoko epeke tupaęž‰ halo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ daĚ±oĚ±la hasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teke ulaęž‰me. Koto teketaęž‰ mo hepeni nane yeni pu halaęž‰ danaęž‰ tupele dau tieke hoki nane ulaęž‰ yako piki da pandaęž‰ tukiki nane yopua ulaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Niki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰taęž‰ koto yako piki da pandaęž‰naęž‰ potaęž‰ pilaluekemaęž‰ Yesu ambaęž‰la ambaęž‰ yapeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ hayeke some Melekisedeke hayeke tupaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ anke teke mea mo Yeni Peaasaęž‰ You Hali na paeke hao halaęž‰me.   
\c 7  
\s1 Yeni peao hayeke hali Melekisedeke  
\p
\v 1 Do Melekisedeketaęž‰ Seileme danaęž‰ kini hali hayekeme. Kutaa make mo hande manda halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi lawaasaęž‰ hali hayekeme. Mo hande Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo hande kini hali tonkopu ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea bepolao da laęž‰kaęž‰la pulu haenaęž‰ do Melekisedekemaęž‰ mandaęž‰ hande peaataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ pimaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ wamo piekeme.  
\v 2 Kutu pieketaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ Melekisedeke paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande da pambolo hataęž‰ mieke alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ kiki yaapo yeketaęž‰ homeke hondotaęž‰ Melekisedeke halaęž‰tiki piekeme. Do Melekisedeke laęž‰laęž‰ biki teke titinaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Tikitiki piki haunaęž‰ kini halie laa laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaa make mo ipikaęž‰ biki Seileme danaęž‰ kini halie laęž‰laęž‰ bikinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kini halie laa laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 3 Koto hali ipikaęž‰ inkiki atekenaęž‰ biki make o atekenaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ biki make o ipikitaęž‰ do natenaęž‰ mendiekeme laa make o ipikitaęž‰ do natenaęž‰ homeekeme laa make otaęž‰ na wape pea ulaęž‰me. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke tupaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pa u halo paęž‰laęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ hali hao halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Nikaęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ kini pealaęž‰ biki tieke ulaęž‰ hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ mo hande aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ bepolao mieke alemanu paeyao kiki yaapo yeketaęž‰ homeke Melekisedeke hondo halaęž‰tiki halaęž‰tiki piekeme. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ koto pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Melekisedekenaęž‰ lombei piki biki tieke wieke yekeeki taa peneme yao ulaęž‰ handaęž‰e.  
\v 5 Mo hande ambaęž‰ hayeke hali Lipae ipikaęž‰ eiyekenaęž‰ eiyeke tonutaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ haliweki ombu hatiki pulu pulu haemekeme. Koto yeni peaasaęž‰ hau piaęž‰tiki pimiki ekitaęž‰ mo Lo Pi laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ opitolo hataęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kiki yaapo alenaęž‰ homeke hondo meaęž‰tiki pimikime. Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ eiyeke tonu ikitaęž‰ homeke hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ hamaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ yekepate kone mo Lipae tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kiki yaapo ale manunaęž‰ homeke hondo meaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 6 Melekisedeketaęž‰ Lipaenaęž‰ tapake hali na hayekepate mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki mieke hali Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ kiki yaapo ale manunaęž‰ homeke homeke lo hondo haleeke ekimanu meataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu leekeme.  
\v 7 Wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi alaęž‰ halitaęž‰ manda halaęž‰pate pa mo wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi alaęž‰eki opitaęž‰laęž‰ halitaęž‰ oto nane halaęž‰me. Koto hautaęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Hande Lipaenaęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ homaęž‰peke yeke haliweki hataęž‰ kone mo hande wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kiki yaapo wikieki manunaęž‰ homeke hondo miaęž‰tiki pimikipate pa mo Baibolomaęž‰ na homeke pa hao halaęž‰ halie laęž‰laęž‰ Melekisedekemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande kiki yaapo alenaęž‰ homeke homeke lo hondo taiti miekeme.  
\v 9 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupiki pi lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ Melekisedeke paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande taiti haleeke yeke ekitaęž‰ Lipaemaęž‰ make haleekeme.  
\v 10 Ekipa pieke yekea. Hande Melekisedekemaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ mandaęž‰ hande pieke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Lipaetaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na mendieke yekepate ipikaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ ateke Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ loke tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pitiekeme.   
\p
\v 11 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Isulai wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Lo Pimanu wieke ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo Lipae tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ tapake haenaęž‰ yeke wiekeme. Do Yeni peaasaęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ e pokemeke ekimanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ na piki otaęž‰ tikitiki pimikaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo taęž‰taęž‰ piki yeni peaasaęž‰ hali na opolo epolo piekeme. Do epolo pieke taęž‰taęž‰ piki yeni peaasaęž‰ halitaęž‰ Etoninaęž‰ anketeke mieke some diaęž‰yekepate mo hande Melekisedekenaęž‰ anketeke mieke some epeekeme.  
\v 12 Kotaęž‰ mo yeni peaasaęž‰ tapake homeke yokaa tapake maęž‰ndaęž‰ haenaęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Lo Pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu make topo peaęž‰peke yaęž‰lieke.  
\v 13 Do alomaęž‰ halitaęž‰ mo Lipae tapake hali na hayekeme. Kutupa make ipikaęž‰ tapake hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hondomaęž‰ oloda paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau na piekeme.  
\v 14 Koto ekitaęž‰ koto hande nikaęž‰ Tekehalitaęž‰ Diuda tapake paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ epeeke ekitaęž‰ niki paeyaomaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me. Mo hande yeni peaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ pi pi leeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do Diuda tapakenaęž‰ biki na leekeme.   
\s1 Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ Melekisedekenaęž‰ anketeke miekeeki  
\p
\v 15 Mo opolo epeeke taęž‰taęž‰ piki yeni peaasaęž‰ some ipikaęž‰ hautaęž‰ mo hande Melekisedekenaęž‰ hau leke piki some yeekeme. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ peneme do yaęž‰laęž‰ handaęž‰e.  
\v 16 Koto ipiki yeni peaasaęž‰ hali haenaęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ pa wekimaęž‰ atekenaęž‰ anketeke minaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ o manaęž‰ pimanu wiekeeki mieke ekimaęž‰ na miekeme. Diaęž‰me mo daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki homekemaęž‰ ipiki yeni peaasaęž‰ hali mea haenaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 17 Do ekinaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ Melekisedekenaęž‰ anketeke mea mo na paelo paęž‰laęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ hali hao halipikie laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 18 Kotaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ honkopu na hake pa alemaęž‰ handaęž‰leke handaa pa nane winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 19 Koto pieke ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo Mosesinaęž‰ Lo Pi wiekeeki manumaęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ tikitiki na yaeyekeme. Kutu pieke yeketaęž‰ niki ipiki teke paęž‰taęž‰ epomono Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Lo Pi wiekeeki otaęž‰ lombei piki panake potaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ wiawayekeme.   
\p
\v 20 Koto potaęž‰ homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰pate mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hali keke ulaęž‰ pi make ulaęž‰me. Mo hande ambaęž‰ haemeke haliwekitaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ haliweki haenaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ dupiki hali keke pi wieke ekimaęž‰ handeteke haenaęž‰ na leekeme.  
\v 21 Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu yeni peaasaęž‰ hali haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ hali keke pi dupa laęž‰ wiekeme.  
\q1 Tekehalimaęž‰ topo na pilieke laa laęž‰ wieke hali keke pimaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Neketaęž‰ bapi paeyaonaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ hali hao halipikie laa laęž‰ ulume leekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Yesutaęž‰ mo niki epeaaluekemaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke ulaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teke hali haenaęž‰yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ koto hali keke pi laęž‰ wiekeme. Koto ekinaęž‰ do panake laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki niki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wiekeeki otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 23 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰piki hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ make paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ dupa paęž‰laęž‰me. Ambaęž‰ hande yeni peao haemeke haliweki ikaęž‰ e minaęž‰paęž‰lao homaęž‰tiki peaęž‰peke yeke handaa ikitaęž‰ eleke eleke haenaęž‰ leekepate  
\v 24 Yesutaęž‰ pa hao haleke handaa ipikaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 25 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wetepe make ame do make mo ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipilimi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ daęž‰taapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ honke latiki puluekemaęž‰ hao halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 26 Koto ekinaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ Yeni Peao Halaęž‰ You Hali hataęž‰ nikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu anaęž‰naęž‰ tambaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikitaęž‰ yako piki hali halaęž‰me. Kutupataęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ o hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ hautaęž‰ hoke hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hau leke na pieke handaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Neketaęž‰ otaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ halie laa otaęž‰ oli hepeni manda nane mini liao haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 27 Koto ekimaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ mandane yeni peao haleme haliweki tupaęž‰ na halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke koto yeni peaasaęž‰ haliweki ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau aęž‰mbaenaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lialuekemaęž‰taęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ lo titinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau ambaęž‰la aęž‰mbaenaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lia halaęž‰tiki pu halemepate Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ na piekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaaluekemaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lia halaęž‰tiki pu halemepate Yesumaęž‰taęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ na pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaaluekemaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ lia halemeke tupaęž‰ ipiki kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme. Koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ paeyaaso hataęž‰ hoto homeke homeke peao paeyaeyekeme.  
\v 28 Hande Lo Pi manumaęž‰ mo yeni peaasaęž‰ you haliweki haenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ pa epe na piki haliweki mea hao halaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo Lo Pi hoki nane hali keke witolo ipikaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeketaęž‰ Yeni Peao Halaęž‰ You Hali haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Eiyeke hoto paeyao otaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na taĚ±leke epea haenaęž‰ yeke maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me.   
\c 8  
\s1 Yesutaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Yeni Peaasaęž‰ You Hali  
\p
\v 1 Ametaęž‰ kotaęž‰ do nikanaęž‰maęž‰ alomaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ dupae. Yeni Peaasaęž‰ You Halitaęž‰ oli hepeni nane halaęž‰ Kini Hali Tiekenaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ale tieke popeke nanemaęž‰ pilaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Kutupa ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yako piki danaęž‰ Yeni Peao Halaęž‰ You Hali halaęž‰me. Koto yeni dataęž‰ halimaęž‰ aęž‰elaęž‰ da diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ dae.   
\p
\v 3 Yeni Peao Halaęž‰ You Haliweki paeyaotaęž‰ pa halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu make lia halaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaenaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lo halaęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ kone nikaęž‰ Yeni Peao Halaęž‰ You Hali make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa halaęž‰laęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ miniki hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 4 Kotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ pa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ hali na halo piaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke. Do kenkenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Lo Pimaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ yeni peao halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ mo pa halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu halolo ombu halememe.  
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ oli hepeni nane halaęž‰ otaęž‰ yeni danaęž‰ mandaęž‰ mea pitemepate pa do kenkenaęž‰ alu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ yeni da paęž‰taęž‰ e pokaasememe. Koto yeni dataęž‰ mo hepeni halaęž‰ otaęž‰ danaęž‰ suĚ±aĚ± suĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰eki homeke halaęž‰me. Mo hande Mosesi haenaęž‰ pieke tupaęž‰ kone pa paęž‰laęž‰me. Mosesimaęž‰ mo hande palai da aęž‰eluekemaęž‰ haenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo danaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰ hau paeyaotaęž‰ mo hande pote paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone otaęž‰ hone wopu wia peaęž‰peke.  
\v 6 Koto haumanu pimikipate ametaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ haleeke yeni peaasaęž‰ etaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ yeni peaasaęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰eki otaęž‰ lombei pikieki haleekeme. Pa ekipeke. Ipikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± ikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witeleme ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰pa hali halaęž‰me. Do Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± laęž‰ u alualu paęž‰laęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wimiki ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do la ulaęž‰eki peaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Panake pi laęž‰ wiekeeki  
\p
\v 7 Mo ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pimaęž‰ eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pa mo panake laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pi make na laęž‰ ulu piaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pu hoeyaemeke ekimanu handolo hataęž‰ do pimanu leekeme.  
\q1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Opuaęž‰pe. Mo Isulai tapake pitaęž‰ Diuda tapake yaapo iki paęž‰taęž‰ ya panake pi laęž‰ wiaęž‰peke nate epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate manutaęž‰ ipulaęž‰me.   
\q1
\v 9 Do panake laęž‰ wiaęž‰peke pitaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ ikaęž‰ meiyeke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ la witaęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰ uaęž‰ tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Koto ikaęž‰ meiyeke tonu mo hande Idiepi kenketaęž‰ ya kikimaęž‰ yokaęž‰ mea tapaaso hataęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ya la witolo pi laęž‰ uaęž‰pate koto hande laęž‰ uaęž‰ pi ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wopu miniki na hake baemekeme. Kutu pimiki handaataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki hoki walaa kiaowaęž‰me laa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Pate pa ame mo Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Mo ipuluaęž‰ nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± laęž‰ ulu polo panake pitaęž‰ dupa laęž‰ ulueke laataęž‰ Mo ya pi ulu pi manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone teke paęž‰taęž‰manu winaęž‰ laotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki manunaęž‰ make wape pealueke. Kutaa IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halueke. Kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ya wandaęž‰hali halimikie.   
\q1
\v 11 Koto nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ da haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ make o ipikaęž‰ ateke hameke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ make pi walolo hataęž‰ alo alotaęž‰ Tekehali hone wipee pi na lelieke.  
\q1 Pa ekipeke. IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ mo natehali wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kini pea pua otaęž‰ hamoko tieke halaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao sikimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± anaęž‰naęž‰ hone wilimikie.   
\q1
\v 12 Kutaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu hoeyaasaęž‰ haumanu paeyaotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pa paeyaalueke. Kutupa make ikaęž‰ hoke hau paeyao IĚ±maęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki hoto paeyao hone yonkaęž‰latiki pulueke laa leekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo panake pi laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande titinaęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰ ambaęž‰eki yaęž‰naęž‰ leekeme. Alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitiki yaalo kukutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ hosiki wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ alupilieke.   
\c 9  
\s1 Alaęž‰taęž‰ na taleke hotekenaęž‰ we mea halaęž‰tiki pimikieki  
\p
\v 1 Mo titinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰eki wieke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ yeni pitolo peaęž‰peke hau paeyaonaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu make la haleekeme. Kutupa do kenkenaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ yako piki yeni da make haenaęž‰ aęž‰eyo haemekeme.  
\v 2 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ palai da homeke aęž‰eyaa haenaęž‰ lemekeme. Mo dataęž‰ tupele pu alu pimikime. Mineke da pandaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰e. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ olaęž‰pake keo pankaęž‰laęž‰ ale make teipolo make kutupa mo teipolo mandataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ palaowa kitiki make wiekeme.  
\v 3 Da pandaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ akaęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ tupele hao pambeekeme. Koto da pandaęž‰naęž‰ bikitaęž‰ Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰e.  
\v 4 Mo Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo totopo piki ale yankaasaęž‰ oloda make mo hande pi laęž‰ u alu paęž‰laęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke bokosi make wiekeme. Mo bokosi pitaęž‰ oloda yaapotaęž‰ timaęž‰ wepia manda nanetaęž‰ kolo kitao aęž‰mbaemekeme. Mo bokosi paęž‰taęž‰ wieke ale manutaęž‰ kolo kanakenaęž‰ maęž‰na pambaęž‰ paleke u make Etoninaęž‰ tumaputaęž‰ pa ipikaęž‰ kone katake haluekemaęž‰ tindiki lu paleke u make mo hande pi ulaęž‰eki wape pieke toopi sopo yaapo make koto ale paeyao panka wiekeme.  
\v 5 Koto bokosi manda nanetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰meeki walolo enisolo leke wepieke ale yaapotaęž‰ wepia handaęž‰ alu pea haenaęž‰ lemekeme. Ipilikaęž‰ popakemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hoke hau aęž‰mbaluekemaęž‰ we holo hayeke ale tikitiki peolaniao wipikime. Pa ametaęž‰ do hau paeyaonaęž‰ tekemanu wopu walaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 6 Mo ale paeyaotaęž‰ koto tupaęž‰ tikitiki yao wimiki alenaęž‰ mo yeni peao halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ mo hande mineke da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ e pokuluekemaęž‰ hoto paeyao puaęž‰tiki aęž‰paęž‰tiki pu haemekeme.  
\v 7 Kutu pu haemekepate mo akaęž‰maęž‰ tupele tukiki nanetaęž‰ otaęž‰ mo Yeni Peaasaęž‰ You Hali homeke peekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piki hautaęž‰ bapi homeke homekenaęž‰ hoto homeke homeke puaęž‰tiki piekeme. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke pa na peekepate otaęž‰ we minaęž‰ paleke peekeme. Koto wemaęž‰taęž‰ mo somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau make mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ na handolo hataęž‰ pimiki hoke haumanu make aęž‰mbaenaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme.  
\v 8 Koto hau manunaęž‰taęž‰ mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Mo mineke da pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pokemeke emanu aęž‰ndaęž‰ pa pokolo haemeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰ tukiki nane polo pumaęž‰ potaęž‰taęž‰ na lumbu pa wiki pa pokaęž‰ pelia hayekeme.  
\v 9 Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do ame halomaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰ hau peneme yawaluekemaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekitaęž‰ do ekinaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu make maęž‰naęž‰ hoteke lia haleleme ekimanu make koto ale manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ lao haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pukimanu otaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ na talenaęž‰ yeke wamo peawapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Koto ale manutaęž‰ pa ne ikali napeke ale o manda loke homeke tandaęž‰paęž‰peke alemanue. Dotaęž‰ pa manda lokenaęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanue. Hau paeyaotaęž‰ wetepe tikitiki yaaluekemaęž‰ yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do manaęž‰ pi pa taęž‰kaęž‰li laęž‰ wiekeme.   
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ we  
\p
\v 11 Ketisotaęž‰ ambaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaa ipikitaęž‰ mo hande Pi Seliapomaęž‰ mea epeeke epeke hau paeyaonaęž‰ Yeni Peaasaęž‰ You Hali halaęž‰me. Kutaa make ame do ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ yeni dataęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ hayeke yeni da otaęž‰ lombei piki alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taleke yeni da halaęž‰me. Mo dataęž‰ halimaęž‰ aęž‰eya haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ da diaęž‰maęž‰ o do wepia ulu kenkenaęž‰ da diaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Ketisomaęž‰ mo da tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ pua mo Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pamba pulutaęž‰ hande kao o sipisipinaęž‰ we Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haluekemaęž‰ na mea peekepate otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ we kone mea peekeme. Koto wemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ deto halo polomaęž‰eki mealaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Mo nanikosi o hali kaonaęž‰ we make mo kao ikiki yankilie ekinaęž‰ yomuneke make koto ale yaapomaęž‰ mo manaęž‰ pi wieke ekinaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ hapu haleme wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ tande laęž‰ kitawaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ manda lokenaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ hapu haleme hau paeyaapeke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰  
\v 14 kotaęž‰ mo Ketisonaęž‰ wemaęž‰taęž‰ koto titinaęž‰ hau otaęž‰ lombei peao hau tieke peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa hone wipee. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo na paelo paęž‰laęž‰ Sipitidi paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±lekeeki ipiki kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ haleekeme. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e anaęž‰naęž‰ pokomono ipikaęž‰ wemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone teke paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ popeke na piki haumanu tandepo halieke.   
\s1 Mo panake laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ we  
\p
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ mo hande panake laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pinaęž‰ honkopu hawaasaęž‰ kaęž‰pa hali hataęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande ambaęž‰ pi wiekeeki oto paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ pimiki hoke haumanu bepolao kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaaluekemaęž‰ yeke ikinaęž‰ homeekeme. Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wi laęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wieke na paetaęž‰laęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ ekimanu minaęž‰yeke piekeme.   
\p
\v 16 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homaęž‰pekeeki teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ hone witolo ipikaęž‰ wekiwandikimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ winaęž‰ laa homolo paęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ telipinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu tameiyaęž‰naęž‰ wape pea wilieke. Kutu piliaęž‰ hoki nane mo weki wandikimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ anke teketaęž‰ mo tameiyaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo handeteke halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ mo sometaęž‰ otaęž‰ homeaęž‰pe laa titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la weilimikie.  
\v 17 Kutu piliepate mo hande tameiyaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ some pa hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo wapenaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na yaalieke. Pate mo some otaęž‰ homeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ wapenaęž‰ laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaalieke.  
\v 18 Koto hau tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ambaęž‰ hande titinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ wiekeeki wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ yaaluekemaęž‰ mo hotekenaęž‰ wemaęž‰ wele peayekeme.  
\v 19 Kutu piekepate titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰lataęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao homeke la la pu mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ la hale hale piekeme. Kutaataęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hali kaonaęž‰ we pitaęž‰ nanikosi we yaapo mea ikali taapunaęž‰ apaęž‰taotaęž‰ mo hisopi tinaęž‰ paleke katake hake pitaęž‰ wepiki wulu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ apaęž‰tao mo we paęž‰taęž‰ peiyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi wieke buka paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ tande laataęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ make tande lo kitaeyekeme.  
\v 20 Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ Mosesimaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki miniki hataęž‰ tolu hamenaęž‰ yeke do wemaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pi tombo walaęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 21 Koto tupaęž‰ kone Mosesimaęž‰ mo palai da manda make tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni puluekemaęž‰ mu halaęž‰ alemanu paeyao make mo hande we tande laa kita kita piekeme.  
\v 22 Otaęž‰ alome. Mo pi ulaęž‰ bukamaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo we homekemaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao yako peaasaęž‰me. Kutaa make we na lombeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau paeyaapeke na yelieke.   
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ we lombeke ekimaęž‰ hoke hau yokawalaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 23 Mo hande palai da make mo yeni puluekemaęž‰ mu haleme alemanu paeyao make oli hepeni nane ulaęž‰ alemanu mandaęž‰naęž‰ uleke handaa mo hande hoteke lia we kitaasaęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ yako peaasaęž‰pate pa mo hepeni nane ulaęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ mo lia halaęž‰laęž‰ hau otaęž‰ lombei piki ekimaęž‰ homeke peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 24 Kotaęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki mandaęž‰ meaaso hataęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ aęž‰emeke Yako Piki Da paęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso na peekeme. Pate ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hepeni nane peekeme. Kutupa ametaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ nikinaęž‰ hao halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 25 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ Yeni Peao Halaęž‰ You Halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hoteke wemanu mea mo Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ bapi homekenaęž‰ tanaęž‰ homeke homeke puaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰pate pa Ketisotaęž‰ hepeni nane pua ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tanaęž‰ eleke eleke halaęž‰tiki na piekeme.  
\v 26 Kotaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tanaęž‰ eleke eleke puaęž‰tiki piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo kenke kini pea wepiaęž‰ dinaęž‰ kone kini pea pua ame do make Ketisomaęž‰ tanda tieke wopu miaęž‰tiki miaęž‰tiki pu halo piaęž‰me. Kutu na pikitaęž‰ ame do paetolo nanetaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homeeke ekimaęž‰ kone mo hoke hau yokawaluekemaęž‰ tanaęž‰ homeke homeke opolo epeekeme.  
\v 27 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao tanaęž‰ homeke homaa hoki nanetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi yokaalu pinaęž‰ handeteke halieke.  
\v 28 Koto tupaęž‰ kone Ketisomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopunaęž‰ hoke hau yokawaluekemaęž‰ lia we halaęž‰laęž‰ hoteke tupaęž‰ hoto homeke homekemaęž‰ homeekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ opolo epolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau yokawaluekemaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo ipiki epenaęž‰ yuwia haleme wandaęž‰hali peteluekemaęž‰ homeke ipilieke.   
\c 10  
\s1 Hoteke wemaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau na yokeekeeki  
\p
\v 1 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo wetepe epolo paęž‰laęž‰ otaęž‰ hau seliapo tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Pa mo koto haunaęž‰ suĚ±aĚ± suĚ±aĚ± tupaęž‰ homeke ulaęž‰me. Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo pi ulaęž‰eki miniki hataęž‰ bapi paeyao hotekenaęž‰ we halaęž‰tiki halaęž‰tiki pimikime. Kutu pimikipate mo hande pi ulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hotekenaęž‰ wemaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pulu polo peleme wandaęž‰hali epeaapeke na yeekeme.  
\v 2 Mo hande hoteke wemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali otaęž‰ yako pea yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumaęž‰ iki yaalaęž‰ peatiki na pulu piaęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ mo hoteke we halaęž‰laęž‰ hau ambaęž‰ kone paelo piaęž‰me.  
\v 3-4 Pate mo hali kao o nanikosi wemaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau otaęž‰ yokawapeke na yeke handaataęž‰ mo bapi paeyao we halaęž‰tiki pimiki ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimiki hoke haumanu paa niminaa tiatiki pu halememe.   
\p
\v 5 Kutu piki hau wieke ekinaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ipuluekemaęž‰ hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoteke we halaęž‰laęž‰ hau pitaęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ hau yaapotaęž‰ hone na ulu pelepate IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ loke hano tikitiki yawaleme.   
\q1
\v 6 Mo hoteke tieke tonkaęž‰naęž‰ yanka halaęž‰laęž‰eki o hoke hau aęž‰mbaenaęž‰ we halaęž‰laęž‰eki make nakanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homeleme laa   
\q1
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰o. Mo nakaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ bukanaęž‰ wape paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ nakaęž‰ ekihau hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pealuekemaęž‰ do halome alome leekeme.   
\p
\v 8 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la leeke ekitaęž‰ dupa Hoteke lia halaęž‰laęž‰eki o pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰eki o yanka halaęž‰laęž‰eki make o hoke hau aęž‰mbaenaęž‰ we halaęž‰laęž‰eki kutu piki hau paeyao mo pi ulaęž‰ bukamaęž‰ peaęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰pate kone nakanaęž‰maęž‰ kotaęž‰ haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homo make hone na pime leekeme.  
\v 9 Kutaa yaapo peao alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰o. Nakaęž‰ ekihau hone paęž‰laęž‰eki pealuekemaęž‰ do halome leekeme. Koto leeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ hau yoka pa mo wetepe epolo pieke panake takaęž‰lake hau mea tiaeyekeme.  
\v 10 Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Atekenaęž‰ pi teliolo hataęž‰ Atekenaęž‰ hone piekeeki paeyao pitolo ipikaęž‰ loketaęž‰ paa pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ hoteke we leke pa hoto homeke homeke halaa paeyaeyekeme. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke haumanu pa paeyao yokaa yako pea hamono laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Ketisonaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau otaęž‰ paeyaalaęž‰me  
\p
\v 11 Mo Diu yeni peao halaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ etaęž‰ nate paeyao pokolo ombu hao halememe. Kutupa mo hoteke we make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto eleke eleke halaęž‰tiki halaęž‰tiki pu halememe. Kutu pu halemepate koto hoteke we halaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau otaęž‰ paeyaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 12 Pate Ketisomaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hoto homeke homeke ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki halaeyekeme. Koto homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ epe alaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ topo na piki pa u pelia halieke. Kutu pu paeyeketaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kiki popeke nanemaęž‰ pitiekeme.  
\v 13 Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki haliweki ipikaęž‰ anke oto nane Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ yeke yu wia handeteke halaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke haumanu paeyawaenaęž‰ la haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoto homeke homeke homeeke ekimaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ wamo peayekeme. Koto ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na paelieke.   
\p
\v 15 Kotoeki kone mo Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ peneme yao la kitolo alotaęž‰   
\q1
\v 16 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ mandane natemanu ipilie dinaęž‰taęž‰ ya pi laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ ulueke laa mo pi laęž‰ witolo pitaęž‰ dupae.  
\q1 Yaka pi ulaęž‰eki paeyao ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ wiaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tekenaęž‰ wape pealueke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\m
\v 17 Pate pa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ apaęž‰taaso alotaęž‰  
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke haumanu o otaęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yeke hoke hau pimiki ekimanu pa ame anetaęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulueke laęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do koto hoke haumanu pa paeyaalaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ mo hoteke lia halaęž‰laęž‰ hau manutaęž‰ paa peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ hamanaęž‰e  
\p
\v 19 Kame tonuo. Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ wemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ potaęž‰ wiawaleke handaa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ hone na wiki pa puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 20 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hondaęž‰ pambomonotaęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ panake potaęž‰ homeketaęž‰ mo tupele dau pondaęž‰paęž‰ lia wiaeyekeme. Koto tupele dautaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ lokee.  
\v 21 Nikaęž‰ yeni peao halaęž‰ hali tiekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali handeteke halaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Koto paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hau homeke miniki halomeke handa make Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulaomeke handa make Ketisonaęž‰ wemaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ hoke hone tekenaęž‰ tande laaleke halomeke handa make mo kila wiki ikalimaęž‰ nikaęž‰ loke tandaęž‰paleke handa make koto halomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa hamanaęž‰e.  
\v 23 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ na tunkulieke hone witolomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone tulaasome alomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu miniki hamanaęž‰ piaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 24 Niki paeyaomaęž‰ nikaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kone pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki puluekemaęž‰ make epeke tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hau pu alualu puluekemaęž‰ make ekipa saęž‰tia alualu pea hataęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe hone umanaęž‰e.  
\v 25 Mo nikaęž‰ Ketiso kametonu ameĚ±leĚ± mombolo halomaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao haleme tupaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lamanaęž‰e. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ yomaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kone hone utia alualu pumanaęž‰e.   
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke hoki na walamanaęž‰e  
\p
\v 26 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pi opua hone witolo hataęž‰ kone hoke hau pa puaęž‰tiki pu haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hoke hau paeyawaenaęž‰ halaęž‰peke we maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate  
\v 27 pa paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo handeteke hapeke hau yaapo homeketaęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Hau maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki epolo paęž‰laęž‰ekie. Maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ liteme wandaęž‰hali tolo paęž‰laęž‰ wele wopu piki ti talaęž‰eki epolo paęž‰laęž‰ekie.  
\v 28 Mo Diu hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ Mosesinaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰eki yambieke handaa mo handaęž‰laęž‰ hali yaapo tepo manunaęž‰ pimaęž‰ otaęž‰ pie lemeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hali paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ na homeke homenaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 29 Kutu piekeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ mo aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ Sipitidi laasaęž‰ pi alo make mo ipikaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaeyeke pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ wetaęž‰ pa ekie hone witolo hataęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke hoki walaa paa pa alemaęž‰ handa yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki hau opolo ipiliekee hone witemepe. Kutu pilie sometaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo litaęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ lombei piki hoke yenki milieke hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 30 Mo yenki meake hautaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pealueke. Hoke yenkitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kone pa halueke laa pi leeke halitaęž‰ niki hone witolomaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ leekeeki maęž‰ndaęž‰ dupae. Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu pilieke leekeme.  
\v 31 Mo deto halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hoke yenki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ taapolo talo peaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ paalaęž‰ piki haue.   
\s1 Wopu takaęž‰lao hone tulao hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 32 Mo hande iki ambaęž‰ haeme ekimanu niminaapaęž‰peke. Koto pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peayaęž‰ hoki nanetaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu wopu mimipate pa koto hau manumaęž‰ iki bepolaenaęž‰ na leke otaęž‰ honkopu hao haememe.  
\v 33 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ mea hao hataęž‰ hoke keke pimanu alo hataęž‰ iki yombua baememe. Kutaa make mo mandane Ketiso yankeke tonu koto tupaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pimikieki handaataęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ niki make mandake linaęž‰ pomanaęž‰e laa pememe.  
\v 34 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo dipula pitimi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homememe. Kutupa make mandane haliwekimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia haeme alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao pake muluekemaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ pemekeeki handemeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ pa otaęž‰ paeyaapeke na yeke epeke alemanu pa wia halomaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ pa epeke tupaęž‰ hao haememe.   
\p
\v 35 Ikaęž‰ aelaęž‰ baasaęž‰ hau na minaęž‰paęž‰lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Ikaęž‰ koto epeke haunaęž‰ epeke yenki tieke milimikie.  
\v 36 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki ambaęž‰la pealuekemaęž‰ make mo ipikaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ alemanu muluekemaęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yopu yu wia hapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 37 Kutu peaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Pa hosiki siki yu wia hao wetepenaęž‰taęž‰ mo epolo paęž‰laęž‰ hali opolo ipuluekemaęž‰taęž‰ hoi hoi na piki opolo ipilieke.   
\q1
\v 38 Koto yu wia halo pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi otaęž‰ tikitiki yao halaęž‰ halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulaalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ pa hao haenaęž‰ lelieke.  
\q1 Kutu piliaęž‰pate pa hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yolaęž‰ pambeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homolueke laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 39 Nikitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰pekeeki alu pinaęž‰ yolaęž‰ pamba hapeke wandaęž‰hali na halomaęž‰me. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hone ti laaso hataęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki mea halomaęž‰me.   
\c 11  
\s1 Hone tulaasaęž‰ haunaęž‰ teke pi  
\p
\v 1 Mo hone tulaaluekemaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ dupae. Hali homekemaęž‰ mo mulueke hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ mea miniki hataęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ honemaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ otaęž‰ ulaęž‰me alo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulao handeteke halaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Ambaęž‰ kiake haemeke wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hone tulao hao haemeke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo hayekeme.  
\v 3 Nikaęž‰ hone tulaasome ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do ya yu paeyaonaęž‰ ulaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pimaęž‰ kone wepiekeme. Kutupa do nikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ mo handaęž‰peke na yeke yeke alemanu mea wepia winaęž‰ leekeme hone witolomaęž‰me.   
\s1 Eipolo Inoko Noa ameda  
\p
\v 4 Mo hande Eipolomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pa halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu haleekeme. Koto hone tulaaso hataęž‰ haleeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Keininaęž‰ pa halaęž‰laęž‰ ale otaęž‰ lombei peakeeki haleekeme. Eipolomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ haleeke ale epeke tupaęž‰ haleeke handaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Eipolotaęž‰ tikitiki piki halie leekeme. Eipolotaęž‰ ambaęž‰ kiaake homeeke yekepate ipikaęž‰ hone tulaeyeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone pa mea u tiao halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 5 Hone tulaasaęž‰eki homeke homekemaęž‰ mo hande Inokotaęž‰ na homeke pa haenaęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hepeni nane mea peekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ pa handaęž‰peke na yeekeme. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Inoko oli hepeni nane aĚ±iĚ± na mea peeke do kenkenaęž‰ pa hataęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homao hayekeme.  
\v 6 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ hone na tulake hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ekipeke. Hali homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰la ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ otaęž‰ halaęž‰me laa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo ipiki otaęž‰ wei moneao haleme wandaęž‰hali iki epeaasaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke yenki molaęž‰me hone tulaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ wetepe epolo pieke hau manutaęž‰ Noa paęž‰taęž‰ kinki piekeme. Koto hau manutaęž‰ Noamaęž‰ handaęž‰peke na yekepate kone ipikaęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi opiekeme. Koto leeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homolo mo wepie leeke kawaso tieke wepiekeme. Koto kawasomaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki make ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ make peteleekeme. Noamaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ leeke pi telia pieke handaa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo hone tulaasemeke halaęž‰laęž‰ tikitiki piki hautaęž‰ Noa paęž‰taęž‰ haleekepate paa pa haemeke mandane wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaeyekeme.   
\s1 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰  
\p
\v 8 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulaeyeke ekimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homa mo hande kuluekee laa pi laęž‰ wieke kenke paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme. Ipikaęž‰ teke da minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo ipiki mateke kenke paęž‰taęž‰ peekeme.  
\v 9 Koto laęž‰ wieke kenkenaęž‰ da maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali leke hataęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hao hayekeme. Ipikitaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ hayekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ wieke tupaęž‰ kone mo Aisaęž‰ke Dieikope yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ make leeke opua miniki hataęž‰ pa palai da paęž‰taęž‰ kone hao haepekeme.   
\p
\v 10 Pa ekipeke. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone pambao wia aęž‰elaęž‰ daonitaęž‰ handeteke hayekeme. Koto daonitaęž‰ mo kukutu peaęž‰peke na yeke pa hao halo paęž‰laęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰ manda aęž‰elaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 11 Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ koke yaalo weki mendiaęž‰peke nate paeyeke yekepate kone ipikaęž‰ hone tulao hayeke ekimaęž‰ weki mendiaęž‰peke yekeme. Seta make weki kenohali wandaęž‰ hayekeme. Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na tunkulieke laa hone bao hayekeme.  
\v 12 Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ teke siki paęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰peke yekepate koto homaęž‰peke somesiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ kone opeeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ pa oli yanaęž‰ hombulankaęž‰ halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ o ikali hounaęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰laęž‰ ulaęž‰ tupaęž‰ haemekeme.   
\p
\v 13 Do alomaęž‰ titinaęž‰ haeme haliwekinaęž‰ Seta peaataęž‰ iki paeyao hone tulaa paleke homemekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰ wieke ekimanu na mimikipate pa papate yolo peeke handaa pa ikaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ homeke handaataęž‰ mokoto yaęž‰laęž‰pate pilaęž‰mee laa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeke homemekeme. Do kenkenaęž‰ koto tapakemaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikaęž‰ da teke do diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate nikitaęž‰ pa taęž‰kaęž‰li halomaęž‰me laa peneme yao lemekeme.  
\v 14 Wandaęž‰hali manumaęž‰ kutupiki pi lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hao hapeke yu weitelememe hone ulumekee.  
\v 15 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande minaęž‰paęž‰laeme kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hone pa na umoneao haemekeme. Hone pa umoneao haemekaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ pa anaęž‰naęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la polo pimime.  
\v 16 Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ do kenke otaęž‰ lombei piki kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ hepeni nane ulaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ puawee hone wimikime. Koto ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ Nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰o laa laęž‰naęž‰yeketaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeekeme. Pa ekipeke. Kodaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pua hapaęž‰peke daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ tikitiki yao wiaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 17 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ makea handeeke dinaęž‰taęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰maęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ eiyeke Aisaęž‰ke lia haluekemaęž‰ peekeme. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ weki wandiki wopu kuluekee laa pi laęž‰ wieke pi miniki hayekepate kone Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki siki homeke kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ lia haluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yaeyekeme.  
\v 18 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ Nakaęž‰ weki Aisaęž‰ke paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ wekiwandiki wopu saęž‰mbaęž‰lawalueke leekeme.  
\v 19 Kutupa Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ Aisaęž‰ke luaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paa mea tiaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone wiekeme. Kutu pieke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homeeke weki paa handaęž‰ miki nono piekeme.   
\s1 Aisaęž‰ke Dieikope make Diosepe  
\p
\v 20 Aisaęž‰kemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulao hayeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki Dieikope Iso yaapo ipiliki paęž‰taęž‰ wetepe epolo piaęž‰ laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ pimanu la haleekeme.  
\v 21 Dieikopemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulao hayeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homaęž‰peke nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ mo Diosepenaęž‰ weki yaapo homeke homeke lo wamo pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau piekeme. Kutu puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ tumapu pitaęž‰ tiao hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaaso yeni piekeme.  
\v 22 Diosepemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulao hayeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homaęž‰peke nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ yeke mo Isulai tapakemaęž‰ Idiepi kenke minaęž‰paęž‰lao polo pimiki ekinaęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wonku piki loke paęž‰taęž‰ peaęž‰peke haunaęž‰ pimanu make la haleekeme.   
\s1 Mosesi  
\p
\v 23 Mosesinaęž‰ inkiki ateke yaapomaęž‰ make ipilikaęž‰ hone tulao haepeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ weki Mosesi mendipiki hoki nanetaęž‰ sumbaęž‰ tepo tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ mondu pankaęž‰ wipikime. Ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke weki seliapo yeke handaataęž‰ mo kini halinaęž‰ pi wieke ekinaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homepekeme.   
\p
\v 24 Mosesimaęž‰ make hone tulao hayeke ekimaęž‰ ipiki weki hali hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo kini halinaęž‰ wanekenaęž‰ weki diaęž‰me leekeme.  
\v 25 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hoke haumanu puluekemaęž‰ hosikimaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa peaęž‰peke yeekeme. Pate kutu piteme tupaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ maĚ±leke liekeme.  
\v 26 Ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Ketiso bikinaęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto haumaęž‰taęž‰ mo Idiepi nane ulaęž‰ mani make kolomaęž‰ wepiki alemanu paeya tapao otaęž‰ lombei paęž‰laęž‰me hone wiekeme. Kutu pieke ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wetepe mulu pieke epeke yenkinaęž‰ hone u hayekeme.   
\p
\v 27 Mosesimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone tulao hayeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo kini halinaęž‰ mineke pankekeeki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeke Idiepi kenke minaęž‰paęž‰layekeme. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo handaęž‰peke na yeke Kodaęž‰ handeke nono pea pa hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiki daĚ±oĚ±la hayekeme.  
\v 28 Ipikaęž‰ hone tulao hayeke ekimaęž‰ mo hande Lombei Pu Pa Yapenaęž‰ sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰ hau kini piekeme. Kutupa mo homaasaęž‰ enisolomaęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ mupeke wekitonu liaamaęž‰naęž‰ lombei pinaęž‰yeke mo sipisipinaęž‰ wemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da potaęž‰ kake ti ninaęž‰ kitaape laa leekeme.   
\s1 Isulai wandaęž‰halimanu  
\p
\v 29 Mo Isulai wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ hone tulaemeke ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Wepiki Dawala Ikali anaęž‰naęž‰ yuma pemekeme. Pate mo Idiepi haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yumimiki tupaęž‰ yumuluaęž‰ patemaęž‰ pu hao mo hande ikalimaęž‰ iki paeyao kili miekeme.   
\p
\v 30 Mo hande Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ nate watake hataęž‰ mo hande Dietiko daoni hopaęž‰liao samaęž‰ pimikime. Kutu pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaemeke ekimaęž‰ mo hande hopaęž‰liao pieke daoninaęž‰ toopi pape tieke londaęž‰laeyekeme.  
\v 31 Mo Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ tapaeyeke kika ikiki hali yaapo tambaęž‰ mieke hali yolo hayeke wandaęž‰ Leihaęž‰pemaęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homu na piki wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± na homeke ipikaęž‰ hone tulaeyeke ekimaęž‰ deteekeme.   
\p
\v 32 Mo mandane ekimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰manu la kionope. Diaęž‰me. Mandane haliweki Kidioni Baęž‰teke Saęž‰misoni Diepita Deipidi Samuele amedamaęž‰ pimikieki make mandane potopede haliwekimaęž‰ pimikieki make wopu mokaęž‰lalo polopate nate leke diaęž‰yaęž‰leke wopu na mokaęž‰lalueke.  
\v 33 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pea mandane kenkemanu bepolayekeme. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tiki tiki hau pitolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kulueke laa laęž‰ wieke ekimanu miekeme. Kutupa mo laeono manunaęž‰ kake aęž‰mbaemekeme.  
\v 34 Mo uleke tieke hake ti tiekemanu honiaemekeme. Mo bainasimaęž‰ liaęž‰pekeeki make wendimikime. Ikitaęž‰ detepiki some hombo yekepate honkopu haemekeme. Kutupa mo aęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ honkopu tieke wopu hao mo hande kenke maęž‰ndaęž‰ tapakenaęž‰ ame tonu bepolaemekeme.  
\v 35 Mandane wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰ make hone tulaemeke handaa ikaęž‰ tapake homemeke wandaęž‰hali Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mea tiao ikaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± haenaęž‰ leekeme. Mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkiliki haliwekimaęž‰ mea tanda halaa homaenaęž‰ leeke haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao haenaęž‰ leeke ekitaęž‰ kiaemekeme. Kutu pimiki ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki epeke daęž‰taa haenaęž‰ lenaęž‰ yeke pimikime.   
\p
\v 36 Iki mandane tapaketaęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ kitata pu make dopitamaęž‰ yombu pimikime. Mandane wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ kiki anke tonkao dipula mea puaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 37 Kutupa mandane tapaketaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pu make mandane tapaketaęž‰ somaęž‰ tukikinaęž‰ tunkulaęž‰ alu peaęž‰tiki pu make mandane tapaketaęž‰ bainasimaęž‰ liaęž‰tiki pu pimikime. Ikitaęž‰ nate hali haemeke ekimaęž‰ sipisipi o nanikosi yonkeleke daumanu yama pominolo haenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homa tiatiki pieke handaa pindipa pomuaęž‰tiki pimikime.  
\v 38 Do kenkenaęž‰ hoke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo koto epeke wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ iki taapunaęž‰ hapeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰ na pieke yekeme. Ikitaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ tulu limiki wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ hapiki kenke paęž‰taęž‰ make pote teaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu make puaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ da manutaęž‰ toopi kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hao haemekeme.   
\p
\v 39 Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaso hataęž‰ pimikieki manumaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ kende wiki biki melememe. Koto pelemepate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kuluekee laa laęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na mimikime.  
\v 40 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ make epeke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ pealuekemaęž‰ hone pambao wiekeme. Koto pambao wieke honetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki homeke diaęž‰ yekepate pa niki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mandake epeaalueke laa hone piekeme.   
\c 12  
\s1 Yesu handa paleke pomanaęž‰e  
\p
\v 1 Mo hande ambaęž‰ haeme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ niki hopaęž‰liao koa leke haleme ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaemekeeki niminaa tiaasememe. Kutu peleke handaataęž‰ do ame halomaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali nikitaęž‰ pa eki pumanaęž‰pe. Do haumanu pumanaęž‰e. Mo niki miniki hataęž‰ meĚ±iĚ±meĚ±iĚ± liaasaęž‰ alemanu paeyao make pa mo taĚ±laęž‰ pelia hasaęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyao londaęž‰laęž‰ mipi bao pomanaęž‰e. Kutaataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ peomono yeke telipalaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±yaęž‰ pulaęž‰ haunaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰pa hao hamanaęž‰e.  
\v 2 Kutu puluekemaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Yesutaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kini pu mea pua anaęž‰ lawalo paęž‰laęž‰ teke hali halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipiki homeke handaęž‰ paleke pomanaęž‰e. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki ti yeke handaataęž‰ pa pinaęž‰ na kiaeyekeme. Diaęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ pua mulu pieke taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hau tieke handeeke ekimaęž‰ mo hande aęž‰kaęž‰tei wape piki tinaęž‰ homaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ meaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ hone maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiekeme. Kutaa ametaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pilaęž‰ ale tieke popeke nanemaęž‰ tilao pilaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 3 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰pa mieke kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tiekemanu hone umanaęž‰e. Mo hoke hau pu haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ honditi pimikieki manutaęž‰ pa hone yonkaęž‰latiki piekeme. Koto piekeeki hone witolo hataęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homo pututumaęž‰ na homo hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke.  
\v 4 Mo hoke hau ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ pelemepate mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ pelemeeki peneme yaenaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ we aęž‰ndaęž‰ na yapaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 5 Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki hamenaęž‰ laataęž‰ do hone u tiaasaęž‰ pimanu la ku halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ na niminake yonkaęž‰lalemepe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupa laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\q1 Ya wekio. Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ neke tikitiki yaenaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wopu wiaęž‰peke. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ neke hando leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homaęž‰peke.   
\q1
\v 6 Pa ekipeke. Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mandane wandaęž‰hali ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki haenaęž‰ laataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ homaęž‰ tiatiki pu halaęž‰me alaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ do kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ mo atekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ weki epeaasaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰e laa puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰paęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo ikaęž‰ mineleme kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki ipikaęž‰ wekiwandiki hamenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki peneme yaasaęž‰me. Ambaęž‰taęž‰ apaęž‰ amedamaęž‰ yombu tikitiki na yaeyeke wekitaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ hayeke yekea.  
\v 8 Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ manaęž‰ laa tikitiki yao hamenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ wekiwandiki na haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ halinaęž‰ wekiwandiki diaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ pake wekiwandiki haleme ekitaęž‰ peneme yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 9 Nikaęž‰ kenke apaęž‰ amedamaęž‰ niki epeaaluekemaęž‰ yombuaęž‰tiki pimikitaęž‰ tanda naa kone ikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homaęž‰tiki pu haomaęž‰me. Mo nikaęž‰ kenke apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu kutu pumeke handaataęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ temoko handeteke halaęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki miniki hamanaęž‰ peaęž‰peke alee.  
\v 10 Nikaęž‰ kenke apaęž‰ amedamaęž‰ bapi wopunaęž‰ niki panisi na peatiki pimipate pa ikaęž‰ hone pieke tupaęž‰ peatiki pimikime. Kutu pimikipate Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki epeomono yeke niki homeke hone witolo hataęž‰ panisi peatiki pu halaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yako piki hau tieke putupa mea halumeke.  
\v 11 Yombitaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ niki taęž‰naęž‰ na pealo paęž‰laęž‰pate kotaęž‰ koto pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰ tikitiki yaeyaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ikitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ mo tikitiki piki haunaęž‰ homu pea puki lopao hasaęž‰ kilikimanu milimikie.   
\s1 Manaęž‰ pi pitaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pi yaapo  
\p
\v 12 Ikaęž‰ lupa wiki kikimanu mea aęž‰meiyao tindipa liao make ikaęž‰ putuputu liki anke yaapo make tindipao daĚ±oĚ±la hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 13 Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ dolaęž‰pake peleme anketaęž‰ otaęž‰ hoenaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate epenaęž‰taęž‰ mo tikitiki piki potaęž‰ manunaęž‰ pu hapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 14 Wandaęž‰hali paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ pelia haluekemaęž‰ taapo hapaęž‰peke. Kutaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ halo pelemeeki tonkaęž‰naęž‰ yako peao haluekemaęž‰ taapo hapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Koto hau na piki wandaęž‰hali homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Tekehali otaęž‰ na handilimikie.  
\v 15 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ hoki walaapaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Iki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰taęž‰pa wilie titi peaasaęž‰ ale maęž‰ndaęž‰ pa opa daeyaenaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ iki paeyao hoeyaapaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu handaęž‰ paleke hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 16 Iki homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yolaęž‰laęž‰ hau piliminaęž‰maęž‰ wopu handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Ambaęž‰ Isomaęž‰ mo hande hoto homeke napeke ne hambolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mupeke wekimaęž‰ miaęž‰peke anke teketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ hone na witolo hataęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa haleeke hau leke na piaęž‰paęž‰peke.  
\v 17 Isomaęž‰ pieke ekitaęž‰ hone wilimime. Ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰naęž‰ epeaasaęž‰ laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ peekepate na miekeme. Mo epeaasaęž‰ hau kinaęž‰e hone witolo ipikaęž‰ apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pua eĚ± alo alo hataęž‰ honke leekepate atekenaęž‰ hone topo pinaęž‰ piaęž‰peke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ wiekeme.   
\p
\v 18 Ikitaęž‰ mo hande Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ otaęž‰ wataapeke yeke Sainai pote paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epemeke tupaęž‰ na opolo epelememe. Koto Sainai pote paęž‰taęž‰ ti uleke tieke make timbaęž‰ make timbaęž‰ ki tieke make po tilipu tieke make  
\v 19 bu kanake litaęž‰laęž‰eki make pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make tieke make koto hau paeyao paęž‰laęž‰ pote paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ iki na opolo epelememe.  
\v 20 Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰make leekeeki opuataęž‰ yaapo peao paa na opuomonoe laa honke lemekeme. Koto paa na opuomonoe laa honke leeke haunaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo hande pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Iki make ikaęž‰ puneleme alemanu maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ make mo pote wataemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ toopimaęž‰ lu homaenaęž‰e laa laęž‰ wieke ekinaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ lemekeme.  
\v 21 Mo potenaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki paalaęž‰ tieke piki haumanu piekeeki Mosesimaęž‰ handolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ± paalaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ pututu tieke paęž‰laęž‰me leekeme.   
\p
\v 22 Ikitaęž‰ koto paalaęž‰ piki pote paęž‰taęž‰ na opolo epemekepate pa mo Saioni pote paęž‰taęž‰ mo deto halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da teke nane opolo epelememe. Koto dataęž‰ hepeni halaęž‰ Diutuseleme dae. Koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo enisolo daoseni eleke eleke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa mombolo halememe.  
\v 23 Ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ mo hepeni nane biki wape pa ulaęž‰ titinaęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ mombaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ eki paęž‰taęž‰ make mo wandaęž‰hali paeyaonaęž‰ pi yokaalu pulu paęž‰laęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ make mo ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ haemeke tikitiki piki wandaęž‰hali epeaeyeke temokomanu paęž‰taęž‰ make opolo epelememe.  
\v 24 Kutaa make ikitaęž‰ mo panake pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰pa hali Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ make ipikaęž‰ tunkulaęž‰ pa pa pu lopeeke wemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Eipolonaęž‰ we otaęž‰ lombei piki laęž‰ witaęž‰laęž‰ we paęž‰taęž‰ make opolo epelememe.   
\p
\v 25 Mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alaęž‰ somenaęž‰ pitaęž‰ na kiaake yopusiki hataęž‰ opuaęž‰paęž‰peke. Mo hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰niaeyeke pimanu laęž‰mea halao haemekeeki na opimiki wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hoeyaasaęž‰eki na wendimikime. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ na wendimiki yeke handaataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ pi la kitaęž‰laęž‰ hali hoki walaa kiaomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ niki make otaęž‰ na wondulumeke.  
\v 26 Ambaęž‰ koto hande tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pi hoĚ±laĚ±ęž‰makemaęž‰ do kenke laęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰maęž‰ peayekepate paa ametaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi laęž‰ witolo alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hoto homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ make do kenke paa laęž‰waęž‰ peaoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ oli hepeni make laęž‰waęž‰ pealueke laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 27 Koto hoto homeke maęž‰ndaęž‰ make laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰eki pitolotaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo laęž‰waęž‰ peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu homeketaęž‰ pa u pelia haenaęž‰taęž‰ pa mo wepia winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ alemanu paeyaotaęž‰ laęž‰waęž‰ laęž‰waęž‰ peao hoelo baalo paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ pi laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 28 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo laęž‰waęž‰ laęž‰waęž‰ peaapeke na yolo paęž‰laęž‰ kilu tombuao halaęž‰eki molomaęž‰me. Koto polomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyaaso hataęž‰ keiyae pi lomanaęž‰e.  
\v 29 Nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoeyaasaęž‰ ti talaęž‰eki yaęž‰leke handaa ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homa pandaęž‰ pea hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ biki mea aęž‰meiyao hamanaęž‰e.   
\c 13  
\s1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ peaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Ketiso tapakemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Ketiso yankeke tonu ameĚ±leĚ± pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰ alualu pu hapaęž‰peke.  
\v 2 Hande leke mineke na handeke wandaęž‰hali kone ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ epenaęž‰ alaęž‰ hautaęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke. Kutu pitolo haenaęž‰taęž‰ pa mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ enisolo halie hone na wiki handaęž‰ mea pitao tapaeyekeme.   
\p
\v 3 Mo dipula haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰eki kone hone witolo hataęž‰ iki hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke. Koto tupaęž‰ kone mo mandane tanda no haleme wandaęž‰hali make hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 4 Wandaęž‰ hapua minaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ hone wopu wia handeteke hapaęž‰peke. Tooli haepekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipilikaęž‰ loke homeke hone ualu pea hapaęž‰peke. Mo suseke haasaęž‰ hau pu make tooli hoeyaaso pake nalaęž‰ hau pu haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pi yokaalu pilieke.   
\p
\v 5 Mani paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki na handeteke haenaęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Koto hau na pikitaęž‰ pa mo ikaęž‰ wia halemeeki manutaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me hone wiaęž‰paęž‰peke. Kutu pulu polomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 IĚ±maęž‰ iki hoki na walo make otaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalueke laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\m
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ aelaęž‰ baaso hataęž‰ dupa lomanaęž‰e  
\q1 Mo Tekehalitaęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali haleke handaa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ na homulueke. Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ekipa hoeyaapeke yeliaęž‰pe alomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Ambaęž‰ mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walao haeme siosi you haliweki hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke. Ikaęž‰ pu haeme haumanu make hone na yonkaęž‰lake niminatiki pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaeme hau hondaęž‰ mea pu hapaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 8 Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ ambaęž‰ make ame make belia make hoto paeyao tapao topo na piki pa homeke hau kone paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 9 Ambaęž‰ na opimi pa taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki pi walimieki manumaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ epeke potaęž‰naęž‰ pulimieki na yolaęž‰ mea paęž‰naęž‰ lapaęž‰peke. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki homekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki hanaęž‰ nokaęž‰paenaęž‰ lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pate paa mo ne na nape laa pi ulaęž‰ hau manumaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Koto hau tolu haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ mo haumaęž‰ iki na tambaęž‰ mu halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Mo Diu wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ e poko haleme haliwekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ oloda paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰ ne manutaęž‰ napeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Ikaęž‰ Yeni Peao Halaęž‰ You Halimaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke hau aęž‰mbaenaęž‰ mo hoteke we mea mo Otaęž‰ Yako Piki Da Pandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea pua halo haemekeme. Pate mo hoteke mindiki manutaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ da hamaęž‰ nane tokulu haenaęž‰ yankaęž‰ baemekeme.  
\v 12 Koto tupaęž‰ kone Yesu make ipikaęž‰ wemaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hoke haumanu paeyaaluekemaęž‰ mo pape tikene homeekeme.  
\v 13 Niki make mandake tupaęž‰ kone mo tikene pua mo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mieke yaalaęž‰ apaęž‰tao mumanaęž‰e.  
\v 14 Pa ekipeke do kenkenaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa hao hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ daoni maęž‰ndaęž‰ diaęž‰ yaęž‰leke handaa mo wetepe opolo epolo paęž‰laęž‰ daoni weitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ laasomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ ale tupaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ halo hamanaęž‰e. Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ biki peneme yao laasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ kiliki ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke halolomaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Epeke hau pualu pu make tambaęž‰ mualu pu pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau yaapotaęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰lapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Do hau yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaenaęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ haue.   
\p
\v 17 Mo ikaęž‰ siosi you haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ homu pea hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homo hapaęž‰peke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ siosi wandaęž‰hali tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyao Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handenaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao waluekemaęž‰taęž‰ timbaęž‰ nate yaaponaęž‰ u na peliki hataęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ temokomanu wopu handeteke hao halememe. Ikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homa telia pu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ lulu hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ e epeke tupaęž‰ pokolo pelemepate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ na homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰eki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ pealieke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo siosi wandaęž‰hali iki na tambaęž‰ milieke.  
\v 18 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ yeni na minaęž‰paęž‰lake wopu peao hapaęž‰peke. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoto paeyao otaęž‰ tikitiki piki hau puluekemaęž‰ taapo halomaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone teketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ otaęž‰ tikitiki paęž‰laęž‰me hone witolomaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± pa aĚ±iĚ± tapaenaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni peamenaęž‰ yeke IĚ±maęž‰ meme pitolo hataęž‰ iki honke alome.   
\p
\v 20-21 Mo sipisipi maęž‰naęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ hali tieke Yesu mo lapaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mea tiaeyaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone mo na paelo paęž‰laęž‰ laęž‰ wieke we paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ e epeke tupaęž‰ pokawamenaęž‰ yeke epeao winaęž‰e alome. Kutupa make mo puki lopawaasaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ niki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ ipiki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tialo polomaęž‰eki pinaęž‰ lomanaęž‰e alome. Ketisonaęž‰ bikimaęž‰ na paelo paęž‰laęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki tieke minaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.   
\p
\v 22 Ya kame tonuo. IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone u tialuekemaęž‰ wape polo pimanu yopu opuaęž‰paęž‰peke laa honke alome. Pa ekipeke. Do IĚ±maęž‰ wape polo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hokulu na wape polome.  
\v 23  Hande nikaęž‰ kame Timodi mo dipula pita opulu bao halaęž‰eki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ opuemenaęž‰ do la kitolo handaęž‰pe. Do IĚ± halo paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki handolo ipulu mandake ipulupekee.   
\p
\v 24 Nikaęž‰ aęž‰taloe pi manutaęž‰ ikaęž‰ you haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make la halawapaęž‰peke. Do Ideli haleme Ketiso yankeke tonumaęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰talo pi iki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaasememe.   
\p
\v 25 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao haenaęž‰e.   